00:09:22,983 --> 00:09:26,718
and to TED, and in fact, when she got onstage,

210
00:09:26,718 --> 00:09:28,665
she said, the first thing she said was,

211
00:09:28,665 --> 00:09:30,819
"I introduced Ricky to Nicky."

