00:10:49,056 --> 00:10:52,109
So the intelligence, instead of being in the device,

244
00:10:52,109 --> 00:10:53,818
we have started today

245
00:10:53,818 --> 00:10:55,930
to move it back onto the cell phone

246
00:10:55,930 --> 00:10:58,300
or closer to the user,

247
00:10:58,300 --> 00:11:00,488
not a particularly enlightened view

248
00:11:00,488 --> 00:11:03,229
of the Internet of Things.

249
00:11:03,229 --> 00:11:06,693
Television, again, television what I said today,

250
00:11:06,693 --> 00:11:09,315
that was back in 1990,

251
00:11:09,315 --> 00:11:10,785
and the television of tomorrow

252
00:11:10,785 --> 00:11:13,108
would look something like that.

